01 Create one New Button similar to old button:-
__________________________________________________

** We have to give only entry inside the App.js inside the App function component or App Class component.
   Code:- <Counter></Counter>
   
02 Make changes for variable Increment:-
__________________________________________________
01 App.js:-Give the entry inside the App component with the values++ increment.
   CODE:- <Counter by={1}></Counter>

02 Counter.jsx:- Inside render() method change the Onclick button incremented value property.
   CODE:- Before:- <button onClick={this.increment}>+1</button>
   After Changes:- <button onClick={this.increment}>+{this.props.by}</button>   
   
03 Counter.jsx:- Change the increment() method.
   CODE:- Before:- increment=()=>{
         this.setState({
             Counter:this.state.Counter+1,

         });
		 
   After Changes:- increment=()=>{
         this.setState({
             Counter:this.state.Counter+this.props.by,

         });
        		 
           
   
   